Subject: [PATCH] drm/i915/bios: add DP max link rate to VBT child device struct
Git-commit: 6dd3104e78943685d5183efe883d83a5f2361bf1
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc1
References: FATE#322643 bsc#1055900
No-fix: c4fb60b9aba9f939d3f8575df23fd8d5958ec6ed

Update VBT defs to reflect revision 216. While at it, default the
expected child device struct size to sizeof the size rather than a
hardcoded value.

V2: Fix bit order (David)

